		"description": "<p>The most common reason for planetouched&nbsp;born to nonmagical parents is having an&nbsp;archdevil somewhere in the family tree. You&nbsp;have the following traits:</p><p><strong>Hellish Resistance. </strong>You have resistance to fire damage.</p><p><strong>Infernal Legacy. </strong>You know the produce&nbsp;flame cantrip. Once you reach 3rd level,&nbsp;you can cast arcane riposte (fire damage&nbsp;only) once between long rests. At 5th&nbsp;level, you can cast heat metal without&nbsp;material components once between long&nbsp;rests. Charisma is your spellcasting ability&nbsp;for these spells.</p>",
